---
import BaseLayout from "../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="总览">
  <main>
    <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="home-title">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">中文优先 · 图解优先 · 静态可部署</p>
        <h1 id="home-title">交互式人工智能图解史</h1>
        <p>
          用可点击、可分步播放、可对比的教学型案例，解释 AI 技术从规则、统计学习、
          深度学习到大模型、RAG 与 Agent 的演化脉络。
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="button primary" href="/chapters/overview/">从总览开始</a>
          <a class="button" href="#mvp">查看章节列表</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="system-map" aria-label="AI 技术演化主线图">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 620 420" role="img">
          <title>AI 技术演化主线</title>
          <defs>
            <marker id="arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse">
              <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="#2f7d5b"></path>
            </marker>
          </defs>
          <path d="M76 210 C150 96 256 90 330 170 S484 312 548 174" fill="none" stroke="#2f7d5b" stroke-width="4" marker-end="url(#arrow)"></path>
          <g fill="#fff" stroke="#d7ddd7" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="32" y="168" width="112" height="70" rx="8"></rect>
            <rect x="180" y="78" width="126" height="70" rx="8"></rect>
            <rect x="332" y="148" width="126" height="70" rx="8"></rect>
            <rect x="472" y="266" width="116" height="70" rx="8"></rect>
          </g>
          <g fill="#17201d" font-size="18" font-weight="700">
            <text x="62" y="207">规则</text>
            <text x="213" y="117">学习</text>
            <text x="359" y="187">大模型</text>
            <text x="508" y="306">Agent</text>
          </g>
          <g fill="#5f6864" font-size="13">
            <text x="58" y="225">搜索 / 专家系统</text>
            <text x="211" y="135">数据驱动</text>
            <text x="363" y="205">RAG / 对齐</text>
            <text x="500" y="324">计划-工具-观察</text>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="mvp" class="section-band" aria-labelledby="mvp-title">
      <p class="eyebrow">推荐学习顺序</p>
      <h2 id="mvp-title">第一版主线：从总览到 8 个交互 demo 和 1 个系统桥接章</h2>
      <div class="demo-grid">
        <a class="demo-card recommended-card" href="/chapters/overview/">
          <small>推荐从这里开始</small>
          <span>Chapter 00</span>
          <strong>00 总览章节</strong>
          <p class="card-meta">约 5 分钟 · 阅读主线</p>
          <p>用 MDX 串起规则、统计学习、深度学习、RAG 与 Agent 的演化主线。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/chapters/search/">
          <span>Demo 01</span>
          <strong>搜索树 / A*</strong>
          <p>切换 BFS、DFS、A*，观察搜索策略如何影响 frontier。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/chapters/expert-system/">
          <span>Demo 02</span>
          <strong>专家系统规则推理</strong>
          <p>选择条件并加入例外，观察 if-then 规则如何产生冲突。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/chapters/bayes/">
          <span>Demo 03</span>
          <strong>Bayes 更新</strong>
          <p>拖动先验与证据强度，看信念如何被证据更新。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/chapters/decision-boundary/">
          <span>Demo 04</span>
          <strong>决策边界</strong>
          <p>比较线性、非线性、过拟合边界，理解数据驱动学习。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/chapters/cnn/">
          <span>Demo 05</span>
          <strong>CNN 卷积核</strong>
          <p>选择 kernel 并推进窗口，观察 feature map 如何生成。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/chapters/attention/">
          <span>Demo 06</span>
          <strong>Attention Map</strong>
          <p>点击 token，比较 Attention 直接连接和 RNN 链式传递。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/chapters/llm-system/">
          <span>Chapter 07</span>
          <strong>LLM 系统地图</strong>
          <p>理解上下文、检索、工具、记忆和评估为什么围绕大模型出现。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/chapters/rag/">
          <span>Demo 08</span>
          <strong>RAG Pipeline</strong>
          <p>观察问题如何经过 embedding、检索、重排、prompt、LLM 和引用答案。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/chapters/agent/">
          <span>Demo 09</span>
          <strong>Agent Loop</strong>
          <p>执行 plan、tool call、observation、revise、final answer 的循环。</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-band" aria-labelledby="overview-title">
      <p class="eyebrow">Overview Artifacts</p>
      <h2 id="overview-title">用时间线、谱系图和图源规范把项目组织起来</h2>
      <div class="demo-grid overview-grid">
        <a class="demo-card" href="/timeline/">
          <span>Timeline</span>
          <strong>AI 技术演化总览时间线</strong>
          <p>按时代串起搜索、规则、统计学习、深度学习、Transformer、RAG 和 Agent。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/lineage/">
          <span>Lineage</span>
          <strong>AI 技术谱系图</strong>
          <p>按范式展示符号主义、统计学习、神经网络、基础模型和 Agent 的关系。</p>
        </a>
        <a class="demo-card" href="/diagrams/">
          <span>Guide</span>
          <strong>图源与导出说明</strong>
          <p>说明 SVG 命名、截图状态和贡献者图源工作流。</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
